<h1>⚠ Low stock alert</h1>

<p>Hello,</p>

<p>A product in the CYNA catalog has fallen below its configured alert threshold. Quick action is
  recommended to avoid stock shortages.</p>

<div
  class='code-box'
  style='background-color: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 16px 20px; margin: 24px 0; border-radius: 6px;'
>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #78350f;'><strong>Product:</strong>
    {{productName}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #78350f;'><strong>SKU:</strong> {{sku}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #78350f;'><strong>Current stock:</strong>
    {{currentStock}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0 0 8px 0; font-size: 14px; color: #78350f;'><strong>Alert threshold:</strong>
    {{alertThreshold}}</p>
  <p style='margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #78350f;'><strong>Detected at:</strong>
    {{detectedAt}}</p>
</div>

<p style='text-align: center;'>
  <a
    href='{{backofficeUrl}}/products/{{productId}}'
    class='button'
    style='display: inline-block; background-color: #4f39f6 !important; color: #ffffff !important; padding: 14px 36px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; margin: 24px 0;'
  >View product details</a>
</p>

<p class='hint' style='color: #9ca3af; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5;'>This alert is sent
  automatically when a product's stock falls below the minimum threshold. To prevent repeated
  notifications, the same alert will not be re-sent within a 6 hour window.</p>

<p>Best regards,<br />The CYNA Team</p>